63) Discover a function that takes an array of numbers as input and returns the sum of all the even
numbers in
the array.
&lt;?php
function sumEvenNumbers($arr) {
$sum = 0;
foreach ($arr as $num) {
if ($num % 2 == 0) {
$sum += $num;
}
}
return $sum;
}
$numbers = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8];
echo &quot;Sum of even numbers: &quot; . sumEvenNumbers($numbers);
?&gt;
output:
Sum of even numbers: 20
